OL,3,CRAF families using Fortnite to
OL,4,Ccommunicate with soldiers abroad
OL,6,Fsoldiers serving abroad are using
OL,7,Fonline video games to keep in touch
OL,8,Fwith their families in the UK, a new
OL,9,Fstudy shows.
OL,11,FResearch led by the Anglia Ruskin
OL,12,FUniversity found children and partners
OL,13,Fof stationed personnel are using
OL,14,FFortnite, Roblox and app games to
OL,15,Fcontact their family member during
OL,16,Fperiod of separation.
