OL,3,CRAF families using Fortnite to
OL,4,Ccommunicate with soldiers abroad
OL,6,FInterviews and focus groups held for
OL,7,Fthe 'Navigating Modern Communication'
OL,8,Fstudy established families use the
OL,9,Fintegrated chat and call functions
OL,10,Fbuilt into games or console to
OL,11,Finteract.
OL,13,F"Because I have an Xbox and my dad has
OL,14,Fa PlayStation, he would take his
OL,15,FPlayStation and we'd play together.
OL,16,FAnd we talked together on the game and
OL,17,Fwe'd just play together on the game,"
OL,18,Fone child said.
OL,20,FAnother said they used Snapchat to
OL,21,Fplay Battleships with their dad.
