OL,3,CRAF families using Fortnite to
OL,4,Ccommunicate with soldiers abroad
OL,6,FFamilies described how internet-based
OL,7,Fmethods made it easier to communicate
OL,8,Fdue to their immediacy and allowed
OL,9,Fparents to be more flexible with
OL,10,Ftimings and communicate on the go.
OL,12,FBut families also shared difficulties
OL,13,Ffinding time to communicate with
OL,14,Fstable internet connections and
OL,15,Fnegotiating different time zones
OL,16,Foccasionally proved barriers.
