OL,3,CRAF families using Fortnite to
OL,4,Ccommunicate with soldiers abroad
OL,6,FSpeaking about the troubles with Wi-
OL,7,FFi, one child told researchers:
OL,8,F"That's the most annoying thing ever.
OL,9,FI'll be talking about something really
OL,10,Fimportant, and I'll be really into it,
OL,11,FI've come to an end, calls off...but I
OL,12,Fcan't remember the start so I can't
OL,13,Fexplain it again. It's really
OL,14,Fannoying."
OL,16,FLead author of the research, Abigail
OL,17,FWood, said online gaming "allowed
OL,18,Fyoungsters to share a hobby with their
OL,19,Fserving parent while spending time
OL,20,Fcommunicating with them".
