OL,3,CRAF families using Fortnite to
OL,4,Ccommunicate with soldiers abroad
OL,6,F"However, it does raise important
OL,7,Fquestions as to whether current
OL,8,Fpolicies and advice for families fully
OL,9,Fconsider the use of in-game chat
OL,10,Ffunctions and the potential risk they
OL,11,Fmay pose to security," she added.
OL,13,FThe study also calls on politicians to
OL,14,Fprovide more information to families
OL,15,Fwith someone serving abroad about
OL,16,Fsafer and securer ways to communicate
OL,17,Fonline.
